def maxProfit(prices, fee):
    n = len(prices)
    buy = [+prices[0]]
    sell = [0]
    for i in range(1, n):
        buy.append(max(buy[i - 1], sell[i - 1] - prices[i]))
        sell.append(max(sell[i - 1], buy[i - 1] + prices[i] - fee))
    return sell[-1]
